description.narrative: In February 2021, the DS PDG approved a Scholarships Improvement Programme (SIP) Target Operating Model (TOM) and an indicative business case which commissioned partial implementation of the TOM, along with the remaining analysis expected to inform a full build of the early capability sought. This business case advances full implementation of the agreed TOM, and includes the rationale required for implementation by June 2023.
